<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-color" style="color:#f5f5f5;font-size:60px"><strong>Staff Hiring Interview Process</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"fontSize":"medium"} -->
<p class="has-medium-font-size">As a hiring manager, one of your most pivotal responsibilities is selecting the right candidate to join your team. These guidelines serve as a roadmap to ensure that your journey through the hiring process elevates the candidates’ experience and upholds our commitment to a fair and impartial selection process. </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:genesis-blocks/gb-column --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:genesis-blocks/gb-columns --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:genesis-blocks/gb-column --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:genesis-blocks/gb-columns -->

