<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized is-style-default"><img src="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-02-113157-b766da690e6e4c9b.png" alt="File folder" class="wp-image-399" style="width:264px;height:auto"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":3,"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"24px"},"color":{"text":"#003057"}},"fontFamily":"Roboto","customFontSize":22} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color has-roboto-font-family has-custom-font" style="color:#003057;font-size:22px;font-family:Roboto"></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:coblocks/accordion -->
<div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion"><!-- wp:coblocks/accordion-item {"title":"\u003cstrong\u003ePreparing for Interviews\u003c/strong\u003e","open":true,"customBackgroundColor":"#003057","textColor":"header-main-bg-color","borderColor":"#003057","customFontSize":16,"lineHeight":1} -->
<div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item has-custom-lineheight" style="line-height:1;font-size:16px"><details open><summary class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item__title has-background has-text-color has-header-main-bg-color-color" style="background-color:#003057"><strong>Preparing for Interviews</strong></summary><div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item__content" style="border-color:#003057"><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Add content…"} -->
<p><strong>Selecting Committee/Panel Members</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>When establishing a search committee/panel there are several considerations for the hiring manager. Use these <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Committee_Panel-Formation-Considerations.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">guidelines</a></strong> when choosing committee/panel members to participate in the search. </li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Understanding Roles and Responsibilities</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Review the<strong> <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Roles-and-Responsibilities.docx" data-type="link" data-id="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Roles-and-Responsibilities.docx">Roles and Responsibilities</a></strong> chart to see how each search committee member can support you in achieving the intended goals of the interview. </li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Committee Checklist</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Provide these items to your committee/panel members: <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Committee_Panel-Checklist.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Committee/Panel Checklist</strong></a>, <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Candidate-Success-Profile.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Candidate Success Profile</strong></a>, <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Applicant-Pool-Evaluation-Summary.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Applicant Pool Evaluation Summary Form</strong></a> , and <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx" data-type="link" data-id="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Candidate Evaluation Form</a></strong>.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Question Selection</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To aid in question selection, utilize the <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Candidate-Success-Profile.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Candidate Success Profile</strong></a>, <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Interview-Question-Matrix.xlsx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Interview Question Matrix</a></strong>, and the <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT-Question-Selection-Guide.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Question Selection Guide</a></strong>. </li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"31px"} -->
<div style="height:31px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></details></div>
<!-- /wp:coblocks/accordion-item --></div>
<!-- /wp:coblocks/accordion -->

<!-- wp:columns -->
<div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column -->
<div class="wp-block-column"></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div>
<!-- /wp:genesis-blocks/gb-column -->

<!-- wp:genesis-blocks/gb-column -->
<div class="wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column"><div class="gb-block-layout-column-inner"><!-- wp:image {"align":"center","id":400,"width":"246px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img src="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-02-113142-13b403f2b6a0470d.png" alt="Three people around a table" class="wp-image-400" style="width:246px;height:auto"/></figure>
