<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:coblocks/accordion -->
<div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion"><!-- wp:coblocks/accordion-item {"title":"\u003cstrong\u003eEvaluating Candidates\u003c/strong\u003e","open":true,"customBackgroundColor":"#003057","textColor":"header-main-bg-color","borderColor":"#003057","customFontSize":16,"lineHeight":1} -->
<div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item has-custom-lineheight" style="line-height:1;font-size:16px"><details open><summary class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item__title has-background has-text-color has-header-main-bg-color-color" style="background-color:#003057"><strong>Evaluating Candidates</strong></summary><div class="wp-block-coblocks-accordion-item__content" style="border-color:#003057"><!-- wp:paragraph {"placeholder":"Add content…"} -->
<p><strong>Conducting Interviews</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Review the <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Conducting-Interviews-Guide.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Conducting Interviews Guide</strong></a> for interview dos and don'ts and modality best practices that will improve hiring outcomes, ensure fairness, and improve candidate experience.&nbsp;</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Checking Perspective/Partiality</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Read the <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Interview-Cautionary-Notes.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>interview cautionary notes</strong></a> for more information.&nbsp;</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Candidate Evaluation</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Choose the evaluation tool(s) that you are comfortable with using to assess candidates.&nbsp;Tools include: <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Candidate-Interview-Evaluation-Form-Choice-3-1.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>Ranking Assessment</strong></a>, <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Candidate-Interview-Evaluation-Form-Choice-1-1.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Qualified Assessment</a></strong>, and <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/Candidate-Interview-Evaluation-Form-Choice-2-STAR-1.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><strong>STAR Assessment</strong></a>.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Align expectations for conclusive answers based on the chosen evaluation tool and candidate success profile.&nbsp;</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Use the <strong><a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx" data-type="link" data-id="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx">Candidate Interview Evaluation Form</a></strong> and<strong> <a href="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx" data-type="link" data-id="https://sites.gatech.edu/administrativeservicescenter/files/2024/05/GT_Candidate-Evaluation-Summary-Comparison_Comptency_Question-Based.docx" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Cohort Interview Evaluation Form</a></strong> as you are assessing candidates.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"44px"} -->
<div style="height:44px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<!-- /wp:spacer --></div></details></div>
<!-- /wp:coblocks/accordion-item --></div>
<!-- /wp:coblocks/accordion --></div></div>
